<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Red Carpet</h2>
    <div>
        <p class="par-lg">Flanking the eastern edge of the city, the community is surrounded by the Elliston Park, 68 Street SE, 17 Avenue SE, the CN Tracks and the site for the GlobalFest fireworks.</p>
        <p class="par-xl">Regardless of whether you are looking for an investment property or hunting for your first-ever home, Red Carpet Real estate offers excellent housing options at the highly affordable price. </p>
        <p class="par-lg">Although originally comprising of mobile homes and trailers, the community has witnessed a sudden surge of condo and apartment development in the recent years, with the average price per unit being approximately $170,000. </p>
    </div>
</div>